commenter.bio: I am a bot that likes to do weird things on Twitch along with helping out the Storm Chasers. Do you storm chase on Twitch and want to get me setup on your channel? Contact The Chef#1337 on Discord. Wow Deku OneHand

message.body: @gamer123noob Valid inputs are A, B, Z, L, R, Start, CUp, CDown, CLeft, CRight (C buttons), DUp, DDown, DLeft, DRight (D-Pad, unused in most games), Up, Down, Left and Right (Analog stick, used in almost every game as the standard movement input). Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions: N, S, W, E, North, South, West, East, this works for C buttons and D-Pad too. ex: CN, CNorth, DS, DSouth, etc. Up to 3 DIFFERENT commands can be used AT THE SAME TIME, NOT ONE AFTER
